{"tid":1036113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老公心理出軌嗎？","createTime":"2019-02-25T04:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T15:34:20.000Z","uid":4187,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4837781f0c3da248a2a5c9cb5ea29c378e7b0008","tid":1036113,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"背景：結婚6年 我33歲 老公35歲 無小朋友 基本上佢都錫我<br />\n<br />\n拍拖一年就結婚<br />\n但結婚後完全無性生活<br />\n問佢 佢話無興趣....<br />\n<br />\n直至第二年 家姐生左小朋友 令我都想要自己既小朋友<br />\n我就同佢傾 咁佢就同我有返性生活 但一d都唔快樂<br />\n好似我求佢先有 我真係越來越唔開心<br />\n之後更發現我不孕<br />\n再發現佢性方便自己搞掂<br />\n我真係好失望<br />\n而有了抑鬱症<br />\n<br />\n之後都無再掂我了<br />\n我都唔想要俾佢掂<br />\n離婚念頭更加大<br />\n<br />\n直至最近發現他wechat<br />\n有認識其他女生<br />\n見到佢問援交要幾錢<br />\n說他要尋求長期女朋友關係<br />\n又說自己需要時自己搞掂<br />\n又說自己已經離婚了...<br />\n<br />\n可能只是玩玩<br />\n但這樣說是什麼意思？<br />\n我真係好失望 覺得佢好恐怖...."},{"pid":"0e25f9cab30d652eff3fc69f6738ca7d78f4ff3f","tid":1036113,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"做愛搵我"},{"pid":"30ca49ba08ff83898089c9a3329fada579048d7b","tid":1036113,"uid":149324,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YBDs6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YBDs6M.png&h=20237cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主幾時變左性又結埋婚仲要食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5d36250320e75967251f68bc10869da1b496d6","tid":1036113,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人介紹到平既箍牙牙醫？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/87194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/87194</a><br />\n2017先year 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019 年紀又大咗又變埋性 <br />\nChing邊到做變性手術？"},{"pid":"02b44c7c107106963e4ba0f0426e4d681b43a01e","tid":1036113,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6f5d36250320e75967251